        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1311",
        "content": "\"I don't think I'll need him any more. I'll miss him, but I think it would be better if I don't have him now. Be good to him, and let me visit him once in a while.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
